AAP.doc:
The resource name of the person to provide information about.

To get information about the authenticated user, specify 'people/me'.
To get information about a google account, specify 'people/{account_id}'.

AAR.name: Search People

AAT.doc: The plain-text query for the request. The query is used to match prefix phrases of the fields on a person. For example, a person with name "foo name" matches queries such as "f", "fo", "foo", "foo n", "nam", etc., but not "oo n".
